Exploratory Data Analysis: Indiegogo

Load Packages and Data

library(tidyverse)
library(jsonlite)
library(cowplot)
library(broom)
library(modelsummary)
library(scales)
library(formattable)
library(fixerapi)
library(pander)
library(qwraps2) # libraries 



indie_clean <- read_csv("indie_clean.csv") # data

Exploratory Data Analysis

indie_clean %>% 
  filter(goal_usd < 100000) %>% 
  summarize(n = n()) # check number of projects with funding goals less than 100,000 USD 
## # A tibble: 1 x 1
##       n
##   <int>
## 1 19287
ggplot(indie_clean) +
  geom_bar(mapping = aes(x = as.factor(state))) +
  theme_cowplot(12) + 
  xlab("Failure/Success") + 
  ylab("Frequency") # compare frequency of successful campaigns versus unsuccessful campaigns 

indie_clean %>% 
  filter(goal_usd < 100000, amount_raised_usd < 10000000) %>%
           ggplot() + 
           geom_point(aes(x = goal_usd/1000, y = amount_raised_usd/1000)) + 
           theme_cowplot(12) + 
           xlab("Project Goal (000's of Dollars)") + 
           ylab("Amount Raised (000's of Dollars)") + 
           ggtitle("Project Goal versus Amount Raised") # Scatter plot of project goal versus amount raised 

ggplot(indie_clean) +
  geom_bar(aes(x = amount_raised_usd/1000000, y = category), stat = "identity") +
  theme_cowplot(12) +
  ylab("Project Category") +
  xlab("Total Funding in Millions ($)") # bar chart comparing overall funding levels for each project category 

ggplot(indie_clean) +
  geom_bar(aes(x = amount_raised_usd/1000000, y = month_launch), stat = "identity") +
  theme_cowplot(12) +
  ylab("Month of Project Launch") +
  xlab("Total Funding in Millions ($)") # bar chart comparing total funding across months of launch

indie_clean %>%
  group_by(currency) %>%
  summarize(n.obs = n()) %>%
  mutate(relative.frequency = paste0(round(100 * n.obs/sum(n.obs), 0), "%")) %>%
  pander() # table to compare frequency of campaigns by currency denomination

ggplot(indie_clean) +
  geom_bar(aes(x = as.factor(year_launch))) +
  theme_cowplot(12) +
  ylab("Number of Projects ") +
  xlab("Year") +
  ggtitle("Distribution of Projects by Year") # bar chart of project frequency by year 

indie_clean %>% 
  group_by(year_launch) %>% 
  summarize(mean_state = mean(state)) %>% 
  ggplot() +
  geom_point(aes(x = as.factor(year_launch), y = mean_state)) +
  geom_line(aes(x = as.factor(year_launch), y = mean_state, group = 1)) + 
  theme_cowplot(12) +
  ylab("Probability of Success") +
  xlab("Year") # line graph mapping probability of success by year
